sue her, not kill her.

333
00:14:12,918 --> 00:14:15,871
Oh, uh, Madeline.

334
00:14:17,256 --> 00:14:19,592
You... You look ravishing as ever.

335
00:14:19,592 --> 00:14:23,095
Thank you, Cliff. I
thought you would like it.

336
00:14:23,095 --> 00:14:24,096
