416
00:19:09,915 --> 00:19:14,920
Now... isn't this wonderful?

417
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:17,422
Yeah...

418
00:19:18,423 --> 00:19:22,427
I wish the guys in the bar could see us.

419
00:19:23,929 --> 00:19:25,430
