release form in the bar.

437
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:17,482
Well, there...

438
00:20:17,482 --> 00:20:19,985
No...

439
00:20:20,986 --> 00:20:21,987
Unless...

440
00:20:21,987 --> 00:20:23,488
