455
00:21:06,698 --> 00:21:09,201
Oh, yeah!

456
00:21:09,201 --> 00:21:11,954
And I'll check my phone messages.

457
00:21:12,754 --> 00:21:15,257
Uh, excuse me?

458
00:21:15,257 --> 00:21:18,260
Well, I get very distracted

459
00:21:18,260 --> 00:21:22,130
