478
00:22:15,934 --> 00:22:17,686
and, uh, give her a call.

479
00:22:19,855 --> 00:22:22,607
Cliff, this is an unbelievable story.

480
00:22:22,607 --> 00:22:24,109
Oh, yeah, Sammy.

481
00:22:24,109 --> 00:22:26,611
