488
00:22:46,014 --> 00:22:48,517
Like Romeo and Juliet...

489
00:22:48,517 --> 00:22:52,521
Rhett, Scarlett...

490
00:22:52,521 --> 00:22:55,023
Heathcliff, Kathy...

491
00:22:57,025 --> 00:22:58,527
Heath, Cliff and Kathy?

492
00:22:59,027 --> 00:23:01,029
